to\": 799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's a part-time model -GQmagazine recently dubbed him \\\"an Olympic prince (and a menswear king)\\\" - a full-timeTaekwondochampion, and he loves the stage.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a part-time model\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"-GQmagazine\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"an Olympic prince\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"a menswear king\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"a full-timeTaekwondochampion\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cunningham is only 21 but has already won a string of medals and became the European heavyweight champion in May.\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.5904823565752082, \"rank\": 0.6760017949993125, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a string\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"the European heavyweight champion\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He arrives in Paris this week as a serious contender for gold, armed with a self-assurance that practically kicks you in the face.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.100914696829529e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a serious contender\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"a self-assurance\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Regardless of whether I win or lose [in Paris],\\\" he says, \\\"I am confident I could go for the next four years and really pick up speed in Taekwondo and conquer this heavyweight division.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.100914696829529e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.358250705229033e-21, \"text\": \"Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next four years\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"this heavyweight division\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am starting to do it now.\\\"\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a child growing up in Huddersfield, Cunningham always wanted to be a sports star, not as a fanciful dream but as an unwavering career goal.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huddersfield_Town_A.F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999977100673121, \"rank\": 1.9060906869041864e-06, \"text\": \"Huddersfield\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huddersfield_Town_A.F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huddersfield_Town_A.F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.5904823565752082, \"rank\": 0.6760017949993125, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports star\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"a fanciful dream\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"an unwavering career goal\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He first tried Taekwondo at six years old, inspired by his dad who competed in martial arts, and aged 10, while doing press-ups and planks at home each evening, they mapped out his Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.358250705229033e-21, \"text\": \"Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his dad\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"martial arts\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"press-ups\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"planks\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic debut\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to move over to kickboxing but that is not in the Olympics, so when we looked at it we thought, no, let us stick with Taekwondo.\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1885, \"end\": 1894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.358250705229033e-21, \"text\": \"Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1825}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Me and my dad worked out that by Paris, that's when I'd be old enough to compete.\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1929, \"end\": 1934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.100914696829529e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's when I decided, I trained every single second I could.\\\"\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every single second\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His dad would encourage him to take on bigger, \\\"scary\\\" fighters and Cunningham would get \\\"beaten up\\\", he admits, but the physical deficit forced him to learn the skills to make up the difference.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2110, \"end\": 2120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.5904823565752082, \"rank\": 0.6760017949993125, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His dad\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"bigger, \\\"scary\\\" fighters\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"the physical deficit\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2179}, {\"ngram\": \"the skills\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2210}, {\"ngram\": \"the difference\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was very lucky to be so self-motivated for the sport, so it made it that much easier to get the techniques down because I just wanted to be the best at them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"the techniques\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He stepped up to the heavyweight division before he was ready but quickly developed into a versatile fighter who could adapt to more powerful opponents.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heavyweight division\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"a versatile fighter\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"more powerful opponents\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cunningham's rapid rise is made all the more remarkable because he lost six months to injury.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2555, \"end\": 2565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.5904823565752082, \"rank\": 0.6760017949993125, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six months\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his first fight of the 2022 World Championships, he felt the anterior cruciate ligament snap in his knee.\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first fight\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2667}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 World Championships\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"the anterior cruciate ligament\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2739}, {\"ngram\": \"his knee\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won the contest with his leg in pieces before losing in the next round.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the contest\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"his leg\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"pieces\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"the next round\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It never changed my path to Paris, for me,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2863, \"end\": 2868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.100914696829529e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my path\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In theory, it made it quite difficult but I never saw it as a big threat.\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theory\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"a big threat\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just thought, this is going to make it a cooler story when I do go.\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 3032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I really knuckled down.\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I saw it as an opportunity to grow and come back an absolute monster.\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3083}, {\"ngram\": \"an absolute monster\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's what I did.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It taught me about myself as a person, it taught me patience, how to really optimise my body in training because anything I did with that leg really fatigued me.\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3189}, {\"ngram\": \"patience\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3244}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3256}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3273}, {\"ngram\": \"that leg\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a blessing.\\\"\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a blessing\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been utterly dedicated ever since, training six days a week, but he has still found time to branch out into the world of fashion.\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six days\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3430}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"fashion\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After signing with management agency Forte, Cunningham has been the focus of editorials in Tank and CircleZeroEight as well as GQ, and he was snapped up by Adidas before the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3516, \"end\": 3526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.5904823565752082, \"rank\": 0.6760017949993125, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}, {\"begin\": 3599, \"end\": 3601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1652171540628657e-27, \"text\": \"GQ\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\"}, {\"begin\": 3628, \"end\": 3634, \"title\": \"http: