onfidence is that a third career is already in his mind.\", \"from\": 4042, \"to\": 4152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4069, \"end\": 4079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.5904823565752082, \"rank\": 0.6760017949993125, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the surest sign\", \"from\": 4050, \"to\": 4065}, {\"ngram\": \"a third career\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4128}, {\"ngram\": \"his mind\", \"from\": 4143, \"to\": 4151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is a fan of mixed martial arts and admires the Ultimate Fighting Championship, a far more violent and lucrative world than Taekwondo.\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4203, \"end\": 4233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UFC_1\", \"score\": 0.9642329294695147, \"rank\": 0.03709380735420987, \"text\": \"Ultimate Fighting Championship\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UFC_1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UFC_1\"}, {\"begin\": 4279, \"end\": 4288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.358250705229033e-21, \"text\": \"Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fan\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4164}, {\"ngram\": \"mixed martial arts\", \"from\": 4168, \"to\": 4186}, {\"ngram\": \"a far more violent and lucrative world\", \"from\": 4235, \"to\": 4273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So after a decade spent planning for Paris, perhaps it is no surprise that Cunningham can already visualise his next move.\", \"from\": 4290, \"to\": 4412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4327, \"end\": 4332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/